BLIN Well see what happens now that the SSR restriction just went into effect with the quick drop that just occurred implementing the alternate uptick rule Rule 201 or the alternative uptick rule has the following features i Short sale related circuit breaker This refers to a factor that would be triggered by a security during any trading day when its market price declines by 10 or more ii Price test restriction duration When the circuit breaker is triggered Rule 201 will apply to short sale orders for that particular security for the remainder of the trading day This may even extend to the following day iii Coverage of securities by price test restriction This regulation covers all equity securities listed on national securities exchanges whether they are traded overthecounter or via an exchange
